import React from 'react'
import { config } from '@gluestack-ui/config'
import { Image, GluestackUIProvider, VStack, View, AddIcon, Button, ButtonIcon, ButtonText, ChevronsLeftIcon, ChevronsRightIcon } from '@gluestack-ui/themed'
import { HStack } from '@gluestack-ui/themed'

export default function Player() {
    return (
        <GluestackUIProvider config={config}>
            <View style={{ flex: 1, backgroundColor: '#1f1f1f', paddingLeft: 5, paddingRight: 5, paddingTop: 30, }}>
                <VStack alignSelf='center' paddingTop={80}>
                    {/* <Box w="$16" h="$16" bg="$blue500" /> */}
                    <Image size="2xl" borderRadius="$3xl" source={require('../img/music dark.png')} />
                    <HStack>
                        
            <Button
              containerStyle={{
                width: 200,
                marginHorizontal: 50,
                marginVertical: 10,
              }}
              title="Clear Button"
              type="clear"
              titleStyle={{ color: 'rgba(78, 116, 289, 1)' }}
            />
                        <Button
                            size="lg"
                            variant="outline"
                            action="secondary"
                            >
                            <ButtonIcon as={ChevronsLeftIcon} />
                        </Button>
                        <Button
                            size="lg"
                            variant="outline"
                            action="secondary"
                            isDisabled={false}
                            isFocusVisible={false}
                        >
                            <ButtonText>Add </ButtonText>
                            <ButtonIcon as={AddIcon} />
                        </Button>
                        <Button
                            size="lg"
                            variant="outline"
                            action="secondary"
                        >
                            <ButtonIcon as={ChevronsRightIcon} />
                        </Button>
                    </HStack>
                </VStack>
            </View>

        </GluestackUIProvider>
    )
}
